title: Suspect in death of 6-year-old Palestinian American boy was obsessed with Israel-Hamas war, prosecutors say
description: Joseph Czuba, the suburban Chicago landlord accused of stabbing 6-year-old Palestinian American boy Wadea Al-Fayoume to death was ordered held behind bars Monday.

title: What Google’s antitrust trial means for your search habits
description: If government regulators prevail against Google in the biggest U.S. antitrust trial in a quarter century, it’s likely to unleash drastic changes that will undermine the dominance of a search engine that defines the internet for billions of people.
